# lib-docs (UFR-022) — INDEX.json + README.md + per-lib LESSONS.md tracked.
# Per-lib snapshots / PATTERNS.md / sources.json / VERSION = untracked, regenerated locally on demand by doc-fetcher + doc-curator agents.
lib-docs/**
!lib-docs/
!lib-docs/INDEX.json
!lib-docs/README.md
!lib-docs/.gitignore
!lib-docs/*/
!lib-docs/*/LESSONS.md
!lib-docs/@*/*/
!lib-docs/@*/*/LESSONS.md

# frontend docs
!museum-frontend/docs/
!museum-frontend/docs/**

